                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": ""
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 14,
                    "line_text": "A temps pour l’insigne faveur",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": ""
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 15,
                    "line_text": "Qu’il me fait de donner sa vie",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": ""
                }
            ],
            "stanza_text": "Nulle fuite. Mais mon Sauveur,\nAssumant mon sort et ma mort,\nVit en Égypte dont il sort\nA temps pour l’insigne faveur\nQu’il me fait de donner sa vie"
        },
        {
            "stanza_number": 4,
            "stanza_type": null,
            "lines": [
                {
                    "line_number": 16,
                    "line_text": "Et sa pensée à mon bonheur",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": ""
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 17,
                    "line_text": "Éternel, et, par l’action",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
